 ======================================================== what ==

 The movie opens with Chun Li narrating her experience growing up
 aspiring to be a concert pianist. As a child, she moves from San
 Francisco to Hong Kong with her family. There, along with piano,
 she learns Wushu from her father, Xiang, who is a well connected
 businessman. One night, her home is attacked by Bison and his henchman.
 Chun Li's father fights them off until Balrog grabs a hold of a
 young Chun Li, forcing him to surrender. As Bison and his men are
 leaving with Xiang, Chun Li's mother tries to stop them. Balrog just punches her.
